Text: CongratulationsJeff Many congratulations on your promotion to CEO We are proud of all the tremendous progress Enron has made under your leadership so far and I am confident you will continue the progressive leadership of the company in your expanded role I wish you personally the very best and wish you the spiritual support to lead Enron to new heights of serving our global community God bless Rick
